  "texts": [
    "Human reviewers confirmed that in several cases these additional labels were indeed reasonable interpretations, indicating that strict accuracy alone does not fully capture model performance in this domain.",
    "A summary of the benchmarking results is shown below:",
    "• GPT-4o-mini: Emotion Jaccard 0.46, Closeenough 10%, Motivation close-enough 61%.",
    "• GPT-4.1-mini: Emotion Jaccard 0.57, Closeenough 30%, Motivation close-enough 59%.",
    "• Claude 3.5 Sonnet: Emotion Jaccard 0.60, Close-enough 42%, Motivation close-enough 61%."
  ]
